r />\n<br />\n俄國、阿拉斯加都有機場可緊急備降<br />\n南極真係有條毛</blockquote><br />\n經阿拉斯加同飛越唔同喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢ge意思係萬一架飛機係北極上空有事都可以去俄羅斯/anchorage<br />\n<br />\n而家因為成本問題 好多航班都已經轉左用雙引擎飛機（長途航班多數都係777-300er) 因為要考慮引擎可靠性ge factor, 所以有規定雙引擎飛機航線附近要有備用機場 就係所謂ge ETOPS  常用標準係架飛機要用一個引擎最多飛3個鐘去備用機場 而某d新ge機型可以有ETOPS-330甚至370 ge認証 但係基於安全問題 南極/南太平洋依然係有限制"},{"pid":"aa3cf6de5925b29afdf3f4534930fd76779c0411","tid":319451,"uid":118943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T03:31:54.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ee66a7592979305286a8a2761633e94434f58d","tid":319451,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:17:45.000Z","msg":"其實南極上空重有polar vortex呢個問題<br />\n唔係話飛就飛<br />\n<br />\nbetween有冇巴打肯入個channel屌鳩佢地<br />\n而家得一兩條友屌緊佢點錯唔係好夠力<br />\n有冇巴肯同我一齊去屌鳩啲戇鳩？"},{"pid":"75d6a0a65373eeb9564f3641675fdc268290e7b9","tid":319451,"uid":5228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:26:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實南極上空重有polar vortex呢個問題<br />\n唔係話飛就飛<br />\n<br />\nbetween有冇巴打肯入個channel屌鳩佢地<br />\n而家得一兩條友屌緊佢點錯唔係好夠力<br />\n有冇巴肯同我一齊去屌鳩啲戇鳩？</blockquote><br />\n咩channel?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53abeee8a0f21603a41012342cec8487c9166507","tid":319451,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:27:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://chem.tufts.edu/answersinscience/relativityofwrong.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchem.tufts.edu%2Fanswersinscience%2Frelativityofwrong.htm&d=tn6kEAKrQafbM6FcrJe3Sf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=50b56542\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://chem.tufts.edu/answersinscience/relativityofwrong.htm</a><br />\n<br />\nIsaac Asimov寫"},{"pid":"41d2762cc0ddd132fb43e2e48054faf7a599dc30","tid":319451,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201